(55, 'Autumnal Posy', '31.08', '24.99', 'Our new Autumnal Posy is a charming and fragrant mini arrangement featuring robusta leaves, eucalyptus, fountain grass, rosemary, wheat, hypericum berries and cerise spray carnations. This posy is a delightful celebration of the sights and smells of autumn, handcrafted to infuse any space with autumn\'s essence. Cut down to size and place in a jam jar to add a touch of rustic elegance to your home or gift to someone special. Our Letterbox blooms may look a little tired after their journey, please give them 24 hours to perk up in a vase to look their best.', '6x Radiant Brown Wheats\n1x Alluring Green Rosemary\n1x Flamboyant Green Fountain Grass\n1x Bountiful Green Eucalyptus Large Leaf\n1x Artful Green Eucalyptus Parvi\n1x Delicate Cerise Spray Carnation\n2x Charming Green Robustas\n1x Vivid Red Hypericum\nVase not included\nSize:  50cm', '\nNext day delivery\n\n\nYour flowers are arranged, hand-packed and delivered by next-day courier directly from our flower emporium.\nYour flowers will be delivered between 8am and 8pm, but if we’re exceptionally busy it could be between 7am and 9pm.\nIf you want to ensure you reach the recipient at home, please select one of our timed delivery options. We cannot guarantee the exact time your flowers will be delivered when you choose our standard free delivery.\nIf we can’t reach the recipient at home, we will leave your flowers in a secure place or follow delivery instructions provided. We cannot guarantee that we will be able to follow delivery instructions on each occasion.\nYou will get an email & sms notification as soon as your flowers have dispatched our flower emporium, and also as soon as they have been delivered.\n\n\nLetterbox delivery\n\n\nYour flowers are hand-packed into our signature letterbox in bud form,to ensure a comfortable route to their destination. They are delivered by next-day courier directly from our flower emporium.\nThe same delivery times, delivery notification